Built `snake/index.html` as a single-file Snake game following the Apple-inspired design system:

- **Layout**: minimal back arrow (←) top-left, title, Score/Best cards, centered square board, D-pad for touch, keyboard hint
- **Colors**: `#fafafa` bg, `#1d1d1f` text, `#6e6e73` secondary, `#0071e3` accent, red apple with green leaf
- **Typography**: `-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif`
- **Buttons**: 44px pill, accent fill, subtle press scale
- **Cards**: white, 14–20px radius, soft `0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)` shadow — no neon
- **Game**: 20×20 grid, speeds up every apple eaten (140→70ms), wall/self collision, tabular-nums score, `localStorage` best
- **Controls**: arrows/WASD, space to pause, on-screen D-pad (hidden on fine-pointer devices), swipe on board, overlay Start/Resume/Play-again flow
- **All UI text in English**
